{"tid":2098412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車仔新作客衫勁似睡衣","createTime":"2020-07-07T12:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T16:14:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b945600002908f2c7406ccbc27bb8e6856cadd7","tid":2098412,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】英超勁旅車路士周二公佈新球季作客戰衣，慘被球迷留言嘲諷「似睡衣」。<br />\n<br />\n車路士官方公佈新球季作客波衫，由「一剔」製造，以深藍色為基調，加入了現代街頭藝術靈感。<br />\n<br />\n新客場戰衣是受到史丹福橋外觀啟發，V領設計，土生木長的藍軍新星曼治（Mason Mount）坦言愛不釋手：「新衫看上去非常搶眼。」<br />\n<br />\n識睇當然睇留言，球迷對新戰衣毀譽參半，有人留言：「要改為做『睡衣戰隊』。」另一人回應：「或者不想其他球隊留意我們，那麼下季就有機會偷雞。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然少部份網民表示喜歡，但也有人認為太似英甲的高雲地利戰衣。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"a49edef9abca1bc40100b1c010c321bff62ed931","tid":2098412,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/805/30039095805/30039095775_600x337.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F805%2F30039095805%2F30039095775_600x337.jpeg&h=95395819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43784275c01b13675deb0a8265c8fbe60f167d8c","tid":2098412,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"3HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49636a85a69640d18aa5ece233b966344e521268","tid":2098412,"uid":2169,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"車仔=香港人<br />\n反車=大69=中共"},{"pid":"93c381adebe8a5d6e736fdea5c54acd8724898c4","tid":2098412,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d7d9e49cd7722dd012e22cfe071229e3077a39","tid":2098412,"uid":35112,"lik